Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 那傢伙…把「神代」送過去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.02,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(685,658)}ちはや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的吧 睫毛小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教她的也是進攻型歌留多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到敵陣里 然後去進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 對手那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己擅長的牌送過去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小千早而言 只有那張牌是一定要搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會贏的 看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.68,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さびしさに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「群寂侵烟舍…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もろともに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「冷山絕人跡…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.53,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こころあてに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朝寒初霜降…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.12,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わすれじの…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「磐石有時爛…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代」的拉鋸戰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,658)}ちはや
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田也開始賭氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是很不想讓小千早的勁頭起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.35,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありあけの…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「殘月深冷夜…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢好強…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…居然跟安田鬥得不分上下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.28,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おくやまに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「霜葉委深山…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.99,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みかきもり…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守卒明篝火…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被搶到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不僅很強…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個非常喜歡歌留多的人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.94,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色潤原野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:48.11,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみがため　をしからざりし…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「昔時為伊故 百死…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.44,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やまざとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歲晚山愈寒…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這看起來很讓人開心啊 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你在玩 所以我才會這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為跟我們一起玩過 所以才會這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:40.33,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,われてもすゑに　あはむとぞおもふ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「川尚同歸處 人定復舉杯」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.95,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬萊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝…指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩歌留多吧 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起變強吧 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能變強的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 太一你呆在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給新打電話了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得告訴他我升上A級了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你說啊 新…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說啊 新…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是綿谷家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 千早啊! 綾瀨千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天升上A級了! 我很努力哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟太一進了同一所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個叫他「小太」的女朋友 你相信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 原田老師也很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 新…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…變得多強了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能別這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 別再打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多那種東西 我已經不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新說了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為歌留多的名人 就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張牌也不會…讓你們拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手是5歲的孩子 我也不會留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們…陪我玩歌留多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝千早 謝謝太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多那種東西…我已經不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為 我們三人能再次相見…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還跟以前一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
